{"title":"重读长征","authors":["张永权"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"重读长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用生命和热血写就的史书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存放于九百六十万平方公"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里的国土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一页一页地重叠起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叠成二万五千里的征途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我把它一页页打开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便禁不住放声朗读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽有呛人的硝烟扑面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却洗亮了我浑浊的眼目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从字里行间走出的英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立在湘江金沙的血涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺进于乌蒙磅礴的山腹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为前进的路标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指引着一个伟大的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，又有雷锋、焦裕禄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔繁森、李润五……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进这支雄壮的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重读长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我眼前的那艰难曲折的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成了警句和真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像阳光和雨露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润出一片茂林佳木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我终于懂得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征是一部世代必读的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我从书页中走出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似补充了缺少的钙质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对新的雪山草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们必须挺起铮铮脊骨"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}